				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Bard vs Enchanter...<a name="50329"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 6 04 2:21 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Just for the h*ll of it when my bard hits 65 I'm going to challenge my 65 enchanter friend to some duelling :p
<br />

<br />
Now this is still a few weeks/months away but I want to know any strats people have for fighting chanters. He has about 160aa points and around 5.5k hp fully buffed. He has reasonable gear and probably around 250mr self-buffed. He is also very good at PvP as both of us and a few others were on Tallon Zek for about three years until we all moved to Luclin.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
