<br />

<br />
I thought that bard mana cannot be stolen. Have you ever tried to steal mana from a bard? I am just interested if it would work. Assuming it would, why wouldn't the bard just FM himself to OOM at the start of the fight? Unless the  fight is outside of the arena, I can't see much reason to have mana for a bard. But then again I am not from a PvP server. 
<br />

<br />
Gather mana is a great AA. Is it insta cast for the chanter? No doubt draining mana would require draining a chanter twice if he can get off gather mana. If that is true, then even if you get the chanter drained first, I think you can count on him having a pretty good shot at getting the bard mezzed at some point. Once the chanter gets the bard mezzed, it can be game over unless the chanter makes a mistake.
<br />

<br />
Those are just my thoughts, but I would like to hear the opinions of chanters and PvPers from PvP servers.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Drumm</span></td>
